Bahrain Authorities Investigate Blast Near British Embassy

-- B y   D o n n a   A b u - N a s r
-- 
2011-12-04T08:44:21Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-04/bahrain-authorities-investigate-blast-near-british-embassy.html
An explosion hit the front of a
minibus parked near the British Embassy in  Bahrain  and
authorities are taking “the necessary legal measures,” the
Interior Ministry said in a posting on Twitter today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
